Yaron,

R&D resources are scheduled until the end of April as follows:
1. Topaz - SDK and certification to First Data.
2. P2PE certification of SREDKey with Card Connect.
3. Spire SP family support.

Any new development work should be prioritized once the above items are delivered.

The "cost" of allocating a resource from either Israel or US can be calculated in 2 ways:
1. Direct cost of a developer - roughly $100,000-120,000 per year.
2. Cost related to the risk of delaying items 1-3 above (impact is much higher)
